_Kamla Bhatt_ [reports](http://kamlashow.com/blog/2009/02/23/oscar-results-
clean-sweep-by-slumdog-millionaire-danny-boyle-ar-rahman-et-al/) that last
evening British and Indian cast and crew of the movie Slumdog Millionaire (a
British film based on a novel set out in India) made a clean sweep at the
Oscars by winning 8 awards out of 10 nominations including the best picture
award.

